x4freetext: The Zr-90 Target in the Form of a Matallic Foil
2.39+-0.05 Mg/Cm**2 Thick and Enriched to 97.8% Zr-90,
Was Located on a Movable Arm 20 Cm from the Target.The
Solid Angle was Determined by a Single 4.75-Mm Diameter
Circular Aperture Directly in Front of the Detector.The
Silicon Detector was Shielded from Neutrons,Beta Rays
And Gamma-Rays by a 1.27-Cm-Thick Copper Housing.
No Particle-Identification System was Found Tobe
